CIRCUIT ANALYZER
----------------

The circuit analyzer is contained in this directory within the circuit/ and circuit_gui/
python modules. circuit_editor.py is a launcher for the PyQt GUI circuit editor/analyzer.

The library is documented using python docstrings, for the most part. There is no real
user guide for the GUI, but its operation should be fairly intuitive to somebody
with a little bit of background in electronic circuitry and analysis.

