DEPENDENCIES
----------------
For the non-GUI analysis library:
	scipy (specifically, scipy.optimize)
	http://www.scipy.org/

For the PyQt4-based GUI:
	scipy (from analysis library)

	PyQt4 (4.2 or later)
	http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/software/pyqt/download

	py.magic (from the py library)
	http://codespeak.net/py/dist/

Once the dependencies are installed, the circuit_editor.py launcher
should run fine as a script (it has a shebang line at the top), or
else by running "python circuit_editor.py" from the console.

